      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Serve the<strong> peri peri chicken breast farfalle </strong>with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
